opis: Kuća se nalazi južno od Omiša, oko 150m od mora. Apartmanska samostojeća vila sa 8 stambenih jedinica, nedaleko od prekrasnih plaža. Kuća je  uređena u mediteranskom stilu sa prostranim terasama i kaminom. Postoji mogućnost izgradnje bazena.Kuća ima 5 garažnih 8 vanjskih parkirnih mjesta. APARTMENT HOUSE NEAR THE SEA The house is located south of Omis, appr. 150m from the sea. Apartment  villa with 8 residential units, near beautiful beaches. The house is decorated in Mediterranean style with spacious terraces and a fireplace. There is a possibility of building a swimming pool. The house has 5 garages and 8 outdoor parking spaces. APPARTMENTHAUS AN DER OMIS RIVIERA Das Haus befindet sich südlich von Omis, etwa 150m vom Meer. Es ist eine komfortable Villa mit 8 Wohneinheiten, unweit von wunderschönen Stränden.Geräumige Terrassen mit schönem Meerblick, Grillstelle, Garagen und mehreren Parkplätzen.
